{"tid":2119791,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實學護應唔應該繼續番工？","createTime":"2020-07-22T09:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T11:44:16.000Z","uid":152654,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f83c602c04d7d687aa32ae89d2f0f85340ca76ec","tid":2119791,"uid":152654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:50:27.000Z","msg":"作為一個學護，其實依家番工都真係淆⋯雖然心底裡明白第時staff左都要面對依家既醫療問題，但無論係醫院定學校對我地既保障都極之皮毛。而ward又繼續要求作為nonessential staff既我地交更番工⋯<br />\n有冇ching內心都有依個糾結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />番工，ncov都驚學咩人做nurse<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔番啦，staff左先番飽佢"},{"pid":"9219b22c4c54244eb4e2ddaf0a2ea53b33fa5466","tid":2119791,"uid":263618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:54:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88b77204ccf6cf2ccd4180973020628712483463","tid":2119791,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:54:47.000Z","msg":"HA當員工係Condom<br />\n公務員凍薪佢就跟<br />\n你自己諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ffa94cc26e05ada579857a72c81d902851428ee","tid":2119791,"uid":52912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:56:15.000Z","msg":"一直出唔到ward<br />\n就一直畢唔到業<br />\n前線唔夠護士，政府就大條道理引入內地護士，平你兩萬<br />\n到時出到ward , grad 到都冇工做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個版圖拱手相讓"},{"pid":"5832d2639ce3af7bc3b675207865fc53c23fb619","tid":2119791,"uid":239905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ffa94cc26e05ada579857a72c81d902851428ee","tid":2119791,"uid":52912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:56:15.000Z","msg":"一直出唔到ward<br />\n就一直畢唔到業<br />\n前線唔夠護士，政府就大條道理引入內地護士，平你兩萬<br />\n到時出到ward , grad 到都冇工做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個版圖拱手相讓"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime"